Without else:

```js
() => {
  if (foo) {
    return true;
  }

  if (bar) {
    return true;
  }

  if (baz) {
    doSomething();
    return true;
  }

  if (x) {
    return true;
  }

  if (y) {
    return true;
  }
}
```

[And here it is without an extra return](https://eslint.org/demo/#) Which cases eslint not to flag it.
